and a failing state.

78
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:03,680
With border conflicts intensifying,

79
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:06,919
we risk military collapse.

80
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:08,159
Dire omens.

81
00:04:08,159 --> 00:04:09,280
Everyone,

82
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:12,840
