84
00:04:16,759 --> 00:04:18,120
If these ill omens hold,

85
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:19,800
can we counteract them?

86
00:04:20,079 --> 00:04:20,839
Your Grace,

87
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:24,199
