93
00:04:34,199 --> 00:04:35,399
would suffice.

94
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:37,824
But His Majesty decreed

95
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:40,560
to wed after securing the borders.

96
00:04:40,879 --> 00:04:42,439
