97
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:45,560
would damage imperial credibility.

98
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,936
If border defenses collapse

99
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,879
due to this change,

100
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,720
who'll bear

101
00:04:52,399 --> 00:04:53,680
the responsibility?

102
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:55,360
If the imperial word

103
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:56,639
is retracted,

104
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:57,920
it'll bode ill.

105
00:04:58,319 --> 00:04:59,519
Everyone,

106
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:01,680
what other auspicious events

107
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:04,720
could avert this disaster?

108
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:07,720
Not necessarily the Emperor's wedding.

109
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:08,879
If someone

110
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:12,600
