163
00:07:12,896 --> 00:07:14,319
to avert calamity and share

164
00:07:14,496 --> 00:07:15,720
His Majesty's burden.

165
00:07:16,288 --> 00:07:17,279
You useless man!

166
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:19,240
How dare you lecture here?

167
00:07:19,328 --> 00:07:20,448
Fabricated charges

168
00:07:20,968 --> 00:07:22,279
need no justification.

169
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:26,279
If Her Majesty weds me,

170
00:07:26,976 --> 00:07:29,199
it'll bless our nation and people.

171
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:31,720
